  "title": "MANAGER",
  "description": "<ul><li>Delegating responsibilities and supervising business operations</li><li>Hiring, training, motivating and coaching employees as they provide attentive, efficient service to customers, assessing employee performance and providing helpful feedback and training opportunities.</li><li>Resolving conflicts or complaints from customers and employees.</li><li>Monitoring store activity and ensuring it is properly provisioned and staffed.</li><li>Analyzing information and processes and developing more effective or efficient processes and strategies.</li><li>Establishing and achieving business and profit objectives.</li><li>Maintaining a clean, tidy business, ensuring that signage and displays are attractive.</li><li>Generating reports and presenting information to upper-level managers or other parties.</li><li>Ensuring staff members follow company policies and procedures.</li><li>Other duties to ensure the overall health and success of the business.</li><li>Abe to work on weekend and public holiday.</li></ul>",
